            "character": "Sam",
            "text": "Whoa there! Watch out, I'm a walking biohazard of artistic expression. You look new! Name's Sam. What's your destination, adventurer?"
          }
        },
        {
          "op": "narration",
          "args": {
            "text": "Her energy is infectious. After she points me in the right direction, I feel a little less like a ghost in these halls."
